<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>MadugundiSpace & Technologies | Premium Tech Solutions</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #00d4ff;
            --secondary: #7000ff;
            --dark: #06070a;
            --dark-card: #0c0e14;
            --light: #f4f4f9;
            --accent: #00ffa3;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; 
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--dark);
            color: var(--light);
            line-height: 1.7;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            width: 100%;
        }

        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(112, 0, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 40%);
            z-index: -1;
            animation: moveBackground 20s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
            will-change: transform;
        }

        @keyframes moveBackground {
            from { transform: scale(1); }
            to { transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        header {
            background: rgba(6, 7, 10, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .brand-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .mini-logo {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(var(--dark), var(--dark)) padding-box,
                        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary)) border-box;
            border: 1.5px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .mini-logo img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .logo span { color: var(--primary); }

        nav a {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 15px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        nav a:hover { color: var(--primary); }

        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 8% 40px 8%;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 10vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, var(--primary) 50%, var(--secondary) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero p {
            max-width: 600px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 16px 40px;
            background: white;
            color: var(--dark);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 800;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: 0.3s;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
        }

        .section { padding: 80px 8%; }
        
        .section-tag {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--dark-card);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary); }
        .card p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 0.95rem; }

        .founder-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0c0e14 0%, #06070a 100%);
            border-radius: 32px;
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .founder-img {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            background: linear-gradient(var(--dark), var(--dark)) padding-box,
                        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary)) border-box;
            border: 3px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden; 
        }

        .founder-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .founder-info h3 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .founder-role { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 2px; }

        @media (min-width: 992px) {
            .founder-box { flex-direction: row; text-align: left; padding: 60px; }
            .section-title { font-size: 3rem; }
            .logo { font-size: 1rem; }
            nav a { font-size: 0.85rem; }
            .mini-logo { width: 40px; height: 40px; }
        }

        [data-reveal] {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        [data-reveal].active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="brand-container">
            <div class="mini-logo">
                <img src="images/logo.png" alt="Logo">
            </div>
            <div class="logo">MADUGUNDISPACE <span>& TECHNOLOGIES</span></div>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#home">HOME</a>
            <a href="#android">TECH</a>
            <a href="#founder">FOUNDER</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <h1 data-reveal>Digital Architecture. <br>Refined.</h1>
        <p data-reveal>High-performance Android development and privacy-centric web ecosystems, engineered for the next generation.</p>
        <div data-reveal>
            <button class="btn" onclick="window.open('https://github.com/madugundishashant-lab/MadugundiSpace-Technologies-/releases/tag/1.0', '_blank')">Get Official App</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="android">
        <span class="section-tag">Engineering</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Android Excellence</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card" data-reveal>
                <h3>01. Performance</h3>
                <p>We utilize Kotlin-first architectures to deliver lightning-fast response times and smooth interface interactions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" data-reveal>
                <h3>02. Ecosystems</h3>
                <p>Deep system-level integration that respects the hardware while providing a seamless user journey.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="privacy" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01);">
        <span class="section-tag">Philosophy</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Privacy by Design</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card" data-reveal>
                <h3>Zero-Knowledge</h3>
                <p>Our applications ensure data is encrypted client-side. We believe in total user sovereignty over digital assets.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" data-reveal>
                <h3>Invisible Security</h3>
                <p>Security shouldn't be a hurdle. We implement advanced protocols that work silently in the background.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="founder">
        <div class="founder-box" data-reveal>
            <div class="founder-img">
                <img src="images/founder.jpg" alt="Shashant Madugundi">
            </div>
            <div class="founder-info">
                <span class="founder-role">Founder & Chief Architect</span>
                <h3>Shashant Madugundi</h3>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">
                    Established at 17, **Shashant Madugundi** founded MadugundiSpace & Technologies to prove that elite mobile software can exist without compromising personal privacy.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">
                    He leads the technical direction, creating a digital space that is as secure as it is innovative.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer style="padding: 60px 5%; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">&copy; 2026 MadugundiSpace & Technologies.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        const reveal = () => {
            const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('[data-reveal]');
            reveals.forEach(el => {
                const windowHeight = window.innerHeight;
                const revealTop = el.getBoundingClientRect().top;
                const revealPoint = 100;
                if (revealTop < windowHeight - revealPoint) {
                    el.classList.add('active');
                }
            });
        }

        window.addEventListener('scroll', reveal);
        window.addEventListener('load', reveal);
    </script>
</body>
  </html>
